http://nwjs.io/

Downloads
Normal flavor

create project folder

create package.json

{
  "name": "desktop-php",
  "main": "index.js"
}

cover npm and nvm

npm install node-php --save

{
  "name": "desktop_php",
  "main": "index.js",
  "dependencies": {
    "node-php": "0.0.1"
  }
}

Ensure php-cgi is installed

sudo apt-get install php5-cgi

webview reference
https://developer.chrome.com/apps/tags/webview



